text: <@U026PHQ3J> - curious, in your opinion how real do you think Swift is.  Do you think Obj-C is officially dead and the future is all swift all the time, or do you think it will remain a side-car and we will forever remain able to continue being old and crotchety while we develop with Obj-C?
no one can change your age <@U0289USNA>, but you must avoid becoming crotchety!
One day I will be an awesome old guy in a rocking chair... Fist raised... Darn you kids!
doesn't swift still require the obj-c runtime? I doubt that will change any time soon
